XmlTagParser

public XmlTagParser(java.util.Set<java.lang.String> optionalEndTags,
                    java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String[]> specialRuleEndTags,
                    boolean specialScriptLogic,
                    boolean ignoreComments)
Construct an xml tag parser with the given options.

Parameters:
optionalEndTags - a set of (lowercased) tags to automatically close when encountered.
specialRuleEndTags - keys are (lowercased) tags that when seen (opened) causes the first existing value (after the first in the array which is the key) to close.
specialScriptLogic - flag for applying special script logic; should be true when parsing html; otherwise, false.
ignoreComments - flag to indicate aggressive skipping over comment data.

Parameters:
